{"tid":1398842,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"遊樂設施最隱蔽的公共空間：奧海城一期","createTime":"2019-08-03T03:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T04:32:17.000Z","uid":96089,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7419eabfe9a7fdb21e16e9faa43c4db5f8e40af2","tid":1398842,"uid":96089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:12:53.000Z","msg":"原來香港有啲咁嘅公共空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊樂設施最隱蔽的公共空間：奧海城一期<br />\n<br />\n奧海城一期該處有三幅休憩空間，面積合共約 7,800 平方米，場地由香港鐵路有限公司管理。公園平台可以於港鐵奧運站接駁或經海帆道、海輝道及櫻桃街前往。記者今日到場觀察，發現公園位置偏遠，並連接高級住宅。由公園入口要走約200米才見到遊樂場設施，當時亦只有一個小朋友在玩樂，另一名大叔則倒頭大睡。同時用地貼出「晨運人士請勿喧嘩」標語。不過有附近住戶指 ，平常不太多人使用公園設施，主要路經公園平台為多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18區新聞/309252/盤點油尖旺私人地公共空間規矩-skypark最嚴-君臨天下-最自由\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F309252%2F%E7%9B%A4%E9%BB%9E%E6%B2%B9%E5%B0%96%E6%97%BA%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93%E8%A6%8F%E7%9F%A9-skypark%E6%9C%80%E5%9A%B4-%E5%90%9B%E8%87%A8%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B-%E6%9C%80%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=bee50758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18區新聞/309252/盤點油尖旺私人地公共空間規矩-skypark最嚴-君臨天下-最自由</a>"},{"pid":"3d826d995f5aece15c51f226ce3122e13f2b930b","tid":1398842,"uid":96089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3f290a2abaafc4bffc5790038cf23e3218047e","tid":1398842,"uid":96089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c003a08ccbf991199925fcb14ea1d18f39fd7d3","tid":1398842,"uid":36761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:45:20.000Z","msg":"奧運 &gt; 南昌 Sell HK V Walk &gt; 柯士甸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\